text: Dione Francisco dos Santos (born 25 July 1979) is a former Brazilian football player. ==Club career== He made his Primeira Liga debut for Vitória Setúbal on 13 March 2005 in a game against Vitória Guimarães. ==Honours== ;Vitória Setúbal *Taça de Portugal: 2004–05 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Vila Nova Futebol Clube players Category:Associação Atlética Anapolina players Category:Vitória F.C. players Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal Category:Primeira Liga players Category:União Recreativa dos Trabalhadores players Category:Associação Atlética Aparecidense players Category:Araguaína Futebol e Regatas players Category:Association football defenders Category:União Esporte Clube players
